         FOR EACH mapa_distrib_ccusto OF item_lista_ccust NO-LOCK:
            FOR EACH criter_distrib_cta_ctbl OF mapa_distrib_ccusto NO-LOCK.
               FIND FIRST tt-cta-pesq NO-LOCK
